{
  "text": "The goitre incidence calculated on the basis of the reference values proposed by Zimmermann et al. [CITATION_1] was the highest in 1994 and was 92.6% and 95.4% (age-and BSA-adjusted, respectively) and was lower at the other time points: in 1999, 18.5% and 15.2%; in 2010, 15.8% and 11.6%; and in 2016, 21.8 and 21.7%.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "4447946"
